      "span_text": "In a previous study, a mixed-mode cation exchange SPE (Waters Oasis MCX) plate was successfully used to extract alfentanil from human plasma with more than 80% recovery.  The use of MCX SPE for extracting both alfentanil and midazolam was successful without major modifications from the previously reported method."
